                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180114-146-victim1044 t18180114-146-viclabel793"></join>. On the 27th of December I was at <placeName id="t18180114-146-crimeloc794">the Swan, public-house, Mile End</placeName>
