                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180114-146-off791 t18180114-146-crimeloc794"></join>; the prisoner asked me for a glass of gin, which I gave him; he followed me out, and caught hold of me in the passage; when he left me I missed my pocket-book.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180114-146-person1046">
